	<center>
		<h1>Arbitrated timestamping service</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
	<ul>
            <li>To maintain a database of timestamped documents, produce a one-way hash of the document</li>
            <li>The arbitrator appends the date and time to the has and signs this concatenation</li>
            <li>The arbitrator stores the concatenation and signature in a database</li>
	</ul>
